thread.title: Miss Hannah Sainsbury
thread.title_full: Physique Management reviewed by Miss Hannah Sainsbury

author: Miss Hannah Sainsbury
title: Miss Hannah Sainsbury
text:
I ordered quite a large order from physique and had a few issues regarding payment.
I called and spoke to a very helpful lady who explained the situation although she could not resolve it.
The order came and was delivered when and where I asked it to be.
Couldn't ask for a more helpful efficient company.
Would definitely use again.
